:0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:27:37.000Z","msg":"昏迷程度以E、V、M三者分數加總來評估,滿分15分,最低3分。<br />\n<br />\n總分15分:為正常。<br />\n總分12分或以上:表示病患需要密切觀察。<br />\n總分8分:表示有腦之病變或損傷。<br />\n總分8分以上:預後及復原情況佳。<br />\n總分7分或以下:病患已呈現昏迷現象。<br />\n總分介於3~4分:認知方面回復之預後較差,且有較高的死亡率。<br />\n總分3分:表示深度昏迷、腦細胞已經死亡,死亡率及未來恢復很差。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://relive.tw/glasgow-coma-scale/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frelive.tw%2Fglasgow-coma-scale%2F&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9SrywfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=d9802839\" target=\"_blank\">http://relive.tw/glasgow-coma-scale/</a><br />\n純粹google，唔識醫學野"},{"pid":"cae850470f3959eb11518d55f305dcb7699cc3f1","tid":1658444,"uid":60434,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:28:03.000Z","msg":"總分7分或以下:病患已呈現昏迷現象。<br />\n總分介於3~4分:認知方面回復之預後較差,且有較高的死亡率。"},{"pid":"b4ba7325729ed060317ed2374942a6cc02e80aff","tid":1658444,"uid":55293,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:28:24.000Z","msg":"3分最低<br />\n3-8分 有機會要插喉吹氣<br />\n唔知個刻pupil size 點<br />\n咁樣打法,同個樣有少少灰,有機會ICH"},{"pid":"0a92c58b38c5ea96b9ef59b78428d2c8963932ae","tid":1658444,"uid":90282,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"648b22fa26a0bd431f95849a51009f1c7ef30b54","tid":1658444,"uid":90282,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"fee955c0dc80e85ecef9f42485d1c62da1fd9160","tid":1658444,"uid":86643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:25:36.000Z","msg":"即係點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:27:00.000Z","msg":"verbal response,eye opening, motor response 各項最高5分，最低1分"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:28:30.000Z","msg":"更正<br />\neye opening 最高4<br />\nmotor response最高6"},{"pid":"983352e5f12da7df2204a9afee77656e48a2c875","tid":1658444,"uid":12583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:29:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.ntuh.gov.tw/neur/%E8%A1%9B%E6%95%99%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99/DocLib/%E6%84%8F%E8%AD%98%E9%9A%9C%E7%A4%99%E8%88%87%E8%85%A6%